I said, "We'll discuss it when I get back."

18
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:25,040
You didn't see

19
00:02:25,040 --> 00:02:27,079
those people in the real estate marketing center.

20
00:02:27,079 --> 00:02:28,680
This is a school district house.

21
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,640
Everyone wants a small-sized unit.

22
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,840
Had I waited for you to come back to decide,

23
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,880
85-square units will already have been

24
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,600
sold out.

25
00:02:33,920 --> 00:02:35,560
Our family can't afford a bigger one,

26
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:37,079
like 120 square.

27
00:02:37,520 --> 00:02:38,840
After this meal, let's gather

28
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,480
the money.

29
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,880
We can't afford

30
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:42,000
the 85 square unit either.

31
00:02:42,000 --> 00:02:43,520
We've saved money for a lifetime,

32
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,960
and when we're about to retire,

33
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,560
you want to buy such a house.

34
00:02:47,200 --> 00:02:48,680
It'll be such a great burden.

35
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:50,800
There are still years to go before retirement.

36
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,880
Besides, the sum of our salaries

37
00:02:51,880 --> 00:02:53,120
are not low.

38
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,880
We have our pensions for the retirement.

39
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:56,079
I'm over 50 years old.

40
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,840
What if I get seriously sick?

41
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,560
What if I get cancer?

42
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,280
Pooh!

43
00:03:01,440 --> 00:03:02,200
It's impossible.

44
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:03,660
We're both in good health.

45
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,840
Besides, we have physical examinations

46
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,640
every year.

47
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,640
What if you or I

48
00:03:06,640 --> 00:03:07,840
have an accident?

49
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,760
Qi Guoqing,

50
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:10,720
are you not going to stop acting like that?

51
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,000
Mingyue is the only child we have.

52
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:13,400
And you don't want to spend money on her?

53
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,080
But it has to be

54
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:15,480
something we can afford.

55
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,160
Dad, Mom!

56
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,320
Mom, the house we live in now is

57
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,800
more than 140 square meters,

58
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,960
and it's enough for us.

59
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:24,490
I really don't need a house.

60
00:03:24,560 --> 00:03:25,920
But when you get married,

61
00:03:25,920 --> 00:03:27,450
will you still live with us?

62
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,840
It's the man's job

63
00:03:28,880 --> 00:03:30,320
to buy a house.

64
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,320
We have

65
00:03:31,320 --> 00:03:32,520
raised our daughter so well,

66
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:35,000
and there's no need for us to buy a house as her dowry.

67
00:03:35,000 --> 00:03:36,520
That's so old-fashioned.

68
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,960
It's not a dowry.

69
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:39,440
A girl must have

70
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:40,570
a house in her hands,

71
