79
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,760
What pressure will you have?

80
00:03:54,920 --> 00:03:56,040
I'm dealing with

81
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,200
the biggest pressure in your life right now.

82
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,000
The biggest pressure

83
00:03:58,000 --> 00:03:59,360
in my life is...

84
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:01,560
Is...

85
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:05,010
As the Mingyue said,

86
00:04:05,160 --> 00:04:06,320
transfer the deposit to others.

87
00:04:06,320 --> 00:04:09,600
Anyway, a small-sized school district house is very popular.

88
00:04:09,600 --> 00:04:10,280
Qi Guoqing,

89
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:12,660
can't you understand what I mean?

90
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,650
Jin Yuxiang,

91
00:04:14,600 --> 00:04:16,360
as long as you are happy,

92
00:04:16,829 --> 00:04:19,040
you can do whatever you like,

93
00:04:19,120 --> 00:04:20,240
but it's non-negotiable

94
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,240
if you want to buy a house

95
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:23,570
at all costs.

96
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,330
I'll tell you this, too.

97
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:27,040
I will buy the house!

98
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:28,960
If you don't want to buy it,

99
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:30,600
we'll divorce and split up our property.

100
00:04:30,600 --> 00:04:31,930
I have to buy this house!

101
00:04:32,320 --> 00:04:33,159
Dad, calm down.

102
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,360
Mom isn't serious.

103
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,080
Dad.

104
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,720
If you insist,

105
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:49,200
then divorce.

106
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,159
Dad! Dad!

107
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:51,760
Let him go.

108
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,080
He's being insane.

109
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:54,640
Sit down.

110
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:56,760
In fact,

111
00:04:57,080 --> 00:04:58,640
