114
00:05:00,880 --> 00:05:02,140
about their children!

115
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,200
Mom.

116
00:05:04,840 --> 00:05:06,440
Mom, you've gone too far.

117
00:05:06,440 --> 00:05:07,360
In any case,

118
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:09,600
