120
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:13,380
You think I don't know him?

121
00:05:13,560 --> 00:05:15,120
He wants to divorce me?

122
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,120
OK. As long as he really wants to,

123
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:20,180
I'll go to the Civil Affairs Bureau with him at any time.

124
00:05:23,320 --> 00:05:23,960
Thank you.

125
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:27,490
All right, the food is here.

126
00:05:27,560 --> 00:05:28,820
Let's eat without him.

127
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:31,120
Don't take what your father said seriously.

128
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:32,120
You still have me.

129
00:05:33,280 --> 00:05:33,720
Well,

130
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,930
