131
00:05:37,840 --> 00:05:39,120
I forgot it.

132
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:41,640
Look how forgetful

133
00:05:41,640 --> 00:05:42,680
you are!

134
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:46,440
You two keep me worried all the time.

135
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:02,480
Mom, try this.

136
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,280
It's better to have a daughter, right?

137
00:06:05,280 --> 00:06:07,760
A daughter always warms her parents' heart.

138
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:09,520
She knows you love it.

139
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:16,480
You eat some more too.

140
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:18,810
You still have work to do in the afternoon.

141
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,600
Mr. Liu called.

142
00:06:21,600 --> 00:06:23,800
He said while Can was at work yesterday,

143
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:24,720
the unmarried young men

144
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:25,840
of the museum

