150
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,490
It's just a uniform.

151
00:06:40,200 --> 00:06:42,080
Keep this uniform on you.

152
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:45,200
It might be too late this year.

153
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:46,840
Next year,

154
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:49,120
take part in the civil service exam,

155
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:49,640
so as to

156
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,920
get a permanent position in the museum.

157
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,250
I'll think about it.

158
00:06:56,200 --> 00:06:58,040
I didn't do very well in study before.

159
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,320
I don't know

160
00:06:59,320 --> 00:07:00,360
if I can do it now.

161
00:07:01,320 --> 00:07:02,960
You didn't study well

162
00:07:03,320 --> 00:07:04,560
because you wasted your time

163
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:05,880
on commercials

164
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,800
and TV dramas.

165
00:07:07,360 --> 00:07:09,360
You have a good memory and you remember things quickly.

166
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,890
It'll be just a piece of cake

167
00:07:10,920 --> 00:07:11,720
for you.

168
00:07:13,440 --> 00:07:14,040
Yes.

169
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,680
You don't

170
00:07:16,320 --> 00:07:17,760
have to be a star.

171
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,200
Besides,

172
00:07:19,200 --> 00:07:20,560
you've already earned

173
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,020
two houses for us already.

174
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,210
We also bought a car.

175
00:07:23,640 --> 00:07:25,840
We also have a little bit of saved money.

176
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,000
By running the small supermarket,

177
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:28,000
your father and I

178
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,880
can make enough money for ourselves.

179
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:30,720
You've kind of

180
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,920
taken good care of us.

181
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:33,840
Our family

182
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,920
doesn't have the luck to be rich.

183
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,080
This will do.

184
00:07:39,040 --> 00:07:40,040
Yes. This will do.

185
00:07:40,159 --> 00:07:41,490
We should be contented.

186
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,280
And I don't have to

187
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,720
worry about you anymore.

188
00:07:45,800 --> 00:07:47,200
If anyone asks me

189
00:07:47,280 --> 00:07:48,540
what my daughter does,

190
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,800
I can answer them

191
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:50,800
with pride.

192
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,440
Stop it.

193
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,800
Let her eat.

194
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:56,060
She still has work to do in the afternoon.

195
00:08:01,360 --> 00:08:03,220
Hello, are you Sun Nian's mother?

196
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,320
You've taken me for someone else.

197
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:07,080
Really?

198
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:10,920
Who are you?

199
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,600
My daughter is not married yet.

200
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,160
Stop your nonsense!

201
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,560
Sorry. Sorry.

202
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,000
She looks

203
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,320
so similar to someone I know.

204
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,200
So I took her for someone else.

205
00:08:19,200 --> 00:08:20,520
Sorry. Sorry.

206
00:08:25,840 --> 00:08:26,440
Mom,

207
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,160
don't be angry.

208
00:08:28,360 --> 00:08:30,160
I've closed up the shop already.

209
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:33,840
OK. OK.

210
00:08:35,240 --> 00:08:35,900
From now on,

211
00:08:36,669 --> 00:08:37,720
let's start over.

212
00:08:38,760 --> 00:08:39,549
I'll listen to you.

213
00:08:39,549 --> 00:08:41,000
From now on, I'll turn over a new leaf

214
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:41,909
and be someone better.

215
00:08:41,909 --> 00:08:42,760
Good, good.

216
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,600
OK.

217
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,050
Your father and I

218
