I'll help you.

223
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:07,980
Don't touch me.

224
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:08,920
You just meet your new friends at the party.

225
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,380
Don't even come tomorrow.

226
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:11,720
Haven't I explained...

227
00:09:11,720 --> 00:09:12,580
Don't touch me.

228
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,680
It was my roommates who dragged me there

229
00:09:14,680 --> 00:09:16,080
to join them in the party.

230
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:17,280
I swear

231
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,360
I just went to have a meal.

232
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,920
You also sang!

233
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,160
If I hadn't seen it

234
00:09:22,160 --> 00:09:22,960
on your friend's Weibo,

235
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,920
you wouldn't have told me about it, would you?

236
00:09:24,920 --> 00:09:26,320
I just sang for a while.

237
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,850
Just get out.

238
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,460
Your presence bothers me.

239
00:09:41,520 --> 00:09:42,650
When will you leave?

240
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,920
After Xiao takes his mother and sister

241
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:45,520
to the hotel,

242
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,720
