243
00:09:49,200 --> 00:09:51,600
Have you used Zhong Kui in "Honor of Kings"?

244
00:09:52,200 --> 00:09:52,840
No.

245
00:09:53,040 --> 00:09:54,840
I can't use his hooking skill well. What?

246
00:09:54,840 --> 00:09:55,680
There is a line in it

247
00:09:55,680 --> 00:09:57,080
that I think is very good.

248
00:09:57,480 --> 00:09:58,120
Which one?

249
00:09:58,480 --> 00:09:59,320
Garbage

250
00:09:59,760 --> 00:10:01,490
