255
00:10:11,400 --> 00:10:12,680
I just say a line

256
00:10:12,680 --> 00:10:13,640
of the game.

257
00:10:14,160 --> 00:10:15,120
What's wrong with that?

258
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:15,640
Whom have you

259
00:10:15,640 --> 00:10:17,100
just labelled as garbage?

260
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,180
I don't want to talk to you.

261
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:25,140
So not cool!

262
00:10:35,920 --> 00:10:36,680
Garbage…

263
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:41,480
Everyone is responsible for garbage sorting.

264
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:09,600
Hi, can I help you?

265
00:11:10,080 --> 00:11:11,360
I'm looking for He Ziqiu.

266
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:11,920
I'm here.

267
00:11:16,680 --> 00:11:17,610
You're Chengzi?

268
00:11:18,280 --> 00:11:18,800
Hi.

269
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,680
My brother said you made a birthday cake.

270
00:11:20,680 --> 00:11:21,920
And my mother sent me to pick it up.

271
00:11:21,920 --> 00:11:23,000
You don't have to come here to pick it up.

272
00:11:23,000 --> 00:11:24,200
I'll bring it to him this evening.

273
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:24,860
No, thanks.

274
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,090
Give it to me.

275
00:11:28,040 --> 00:11:28,880
Go inside

276
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:30,810
and get that double-layered cake.

277
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:33,600
Coffee?

278
00:11:35,960 --> 00:11:36,490
How much?

279
00:11:36,800 --> 00:11:38,240
It's on the house.

280
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:40,280
I mean how much the cake is.

281
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,040
It's also free of charge.

282
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:42,640
My mom said

283
00:11:42,920 --> 00:11:43,850
I must pay for it.

284
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:45,770
After all, you're in business.

285
00:11:46,080 --> 00:11:46,610
How much?

286
00:11:47,440 --> 00:11:49,160
Then you go back and tell your mother that

287
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:51,490
I don't charge to make a cake for Ling Xiao.

288
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:53,680
Here. Hold stably.

289
00:11:54,800 --> 00:11:55,600
My mother said

